                        <div class="secchkPanel" id="secchkPanel">
                            <span class="CheckedPanel" id="panel502" title="层析">层析</span><span class="unCheckPanel" id="panel237" title="单质钠" >单质钠</span><span class="unCheckPanel" id="panel490" title="化学实验的基本操作" >化学实验的基本操作</span>
